name: Fuck the dollar, give me your tezos - PART 4
description:
On this occasion we can see Osama Bin Laden crying over the death of our protagonist in a palace after the war. We also find a new character from the collection on the left side. On the right side we have Dr Zoidberg who won the vote via twitter. To find out more about this collection, look for me on twitter and enter the discord group. @Matiaslaplata
Drawing made on September 9, 2021
